OL,3,CCo-op announces #70m plans to create
OL,4,Cthousands of apprenticeships
OL,6,FThe Co-op has announced plans to
OL,7,Fcreate thousands of new
OL,8,Fapprenticeships in the next few years.
OL,10,FThe retail giant gave details of a #70
OL,11,Fmillion commitment through its Levy
OL,12,FShare service to create 7,000 matched
OL,13,Fapprenticeships by 2030.
OL,15,FThe scheme enables levy-paying
OL,16,Femployers to transfer unused
OL,17,Fapprenticeship levy funds to
OL,18,Fbusinesses, charities, and community
OL,19,Forganisations.
