OL,3,CCo-op announces #70m plans to create
OL,4,Cthousands of apprenticeships
OL,6,F"Four years on, alongside our
OL,7,Fcontributing partners, we've already
OL,8,Fchannelled #40 million into thousands
OL,9,Fof life-changing apprenticeships, and
OL,10,Ftoday we're going further, committing
OL,11,F#70 million to create 7,000
OL,12,Fapprenticeships by 2030."
OL,14,FThe Co-op called for socioeconomic
OL,15,Fbackground data for apprenticeships to
OL,16,Fbe collected, warning that without it,
OL,17,Fthe system risked leaving some groups
OL,18,Fbehind.
